@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_unzjmu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.98
    v2 = (0.37 * (wp.cos(v2 + 0.06) * v2))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v1 + 0.56) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.47)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.82 * v1 + 0.10)) - 0.18)
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp(tmp) - wp.sin((tmp + 0.72 + v2 + 0.17)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
